	(descr "Custom sandwich mount for Neutrik NC3MXX 3-pin male XLR chassis connector. Solder-cup pitch 7.62mm. Three 8mm-long pads (2mm wide) at board XLR edge: pin1 (GND) FRONT x=1.90mm, pin2 (P2) FRONT x=9.52mm, pin3 (P3) BACK x=5.71mm. Origin = board XLR edge / left corner, pads extend from y=0 (edge) to y=8mm.")
